node.text:
Here they are! Our contestants still on the Road to Orlando 👑

Voting to help decide our Top 20 Miss #HootersPageant contestants starts tomorrow. Keep an eye on our stories for details!

node.text:
We can’t believe our Miss Hooters Pageant is only TWO DAYS AWAY. 👑

We’ll be hosting a viewing party at your local Hooters so we hope you’ll come watch with us! Head to the link in our bio for more info.

node.text:
Do you have your Pageant game plan ready? 

Tickets are on sale now for our Miss Hooters Pageant in Orlando on 7/29! But if you can’t make it, we’ll be streaming all the action live at your local Hooters. 

Head to the link in our bio for all the details!
